I recall a game I played way back when I first started. We had a Nasus top, but he never appeared for anything, so much so that I thought it was a 4v5 and things were not going well for us.

Nasus in a nutshell. "Okay, got enough stacks and I'm built as a full-tank, time to wreck face."
